name: Moth Lectern
description:
Moth search for the light to mate, oh yes they'll need it so much, once there's only moon for moth to find it's way from dark. 
Then it appears the first light, a warm light enough to warmth our sight, then the second light come in unusual form, the third light appears brighter than the moon, and so the Moth have their way to those new source. 

Let there be light they said, it will be fun they said.
